## Employment and Social Development Canada – System Administrator Resources

### Tender Name (English) / Nom de l’opération (Français)
Employment and Social Development Canada – System Administrator Resources

### Reference Number / Numéro de référence
CB-9350-14734520

### Tender Status / Statut de PAN
Expired / Expiré

### Tender Description

- The Contracting Authority, Employment and Social Development Canada (ESDC) is soliciting for System Administrator, Level 1 and Level 2, on an "as and when requested" basis to support ESDC in delivering various IT services across Canada.
- The resources shall be required, proposed, and assessed at the Task Authorization (TA) level.
- DSFC operating on the Shared Services Canada region

### Mandatory Requirements / Exigences obligatoires

- Common PS SRCL #02 Security Requirement applies
- Minimum Corporate Security Required: Designated Organization Screening (DOS)
- Minimum Personnel Security Required: Enhanced Reliability

### Contact Information

- Karine Chamberland (NC-SOLICITATIONS-GD@hrsdc-rhdcc.gc.ca)
- Phone: 111-111-1111
- Address: 140 Prom. du Portage, Gatineau, QC K1A 0J9

### Tender Delivery Regions / Régions du motif de l'opération

* National Capital Region
* Alberta
* British Columbia
* Manitoba
* Newfoundland and Labrador
* Northwest Territories
* Nova Scotia
* Ontario
* Prince Edward Island
* Quebec
* Saskatchewan

### Closing Date / Date d’échéance
2023-11-01T14:00:00
